    @Deprecated
public class PortConfigurer
extends Query
implements QueryListener
    Deprecated.
    This class is no longer used. Use PortConfigurerDialog.
    This class is an editor to configure the ports of an object. It supports setting their input, output, and multiport properties, and adding and removing ports. Only ports that extend the TypedIOPort class are listed, since more primitive ports cannot be configured in this way.
    Since:
    Ptolemy II 1.0
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    Steve Neuendorffer and Edward A. Lee
    See Also:
    Configurer, Serialized Form
    Pt.AcceptedRating:
    Red (neuendor)
    Pt.ProposedRating:
    Yellow (eal)
